
                                 KD:M Typography
                                    of Death

Use the following cheatsheet to implement KD:M icons using the API's unique 
'kdm_manager_font' attribute:

 - Activation (lightning)
    <font class="kdm_manager_font">A</font>
 - Endeavor (asterisk)
    <font class="kdm_manager_font">E</font>
 - Movement (chess knight)
    <font class="kdm_manager_font">M</font>
 - Reaction (monster reaction; R diamond)
    <font class="kdm_manager_font">R</font>
 - Shield (for rules text; not gear cards)
    <font class="inline_shield">1</font>
 - Story Event (book)
    <font class="kdm_manager_font">S</font>


Deck icons:

 - Fighting Art
    <span class="kd deck_icon" deck="FA">FA</span>
 - Pattern
    <span class="kd deck_icon kdm_manager_font" deck="p">XX</span>
 - Secret Fighting Art
    <span class="kd deck_icon" deck="SF">SF</span>


HTML entities:

 - Affinity blocks (e.g. inline with rules or other descriptive text)
    - Affinity RED:  <font class="kd affinity_red_text" >&#9724;</font>
    - Affinity BLUE:  <font class="kd affinity_blue_text" >&#9724;</font>
    - Affinity GREEN:  <font class="kd affinity_green_text" >&#9724;</font>
 - Star (as in monster level)
    &#9733;
